data.meta_description:
148 likes, 11 comments - manningsumner on March 16, 2024: "S2, Ep 5. Elev8te: Yourself, Business, and Team: Manning Sumner and Angel Bajana 

In this episode of The Big Dawgs podcast, I welcome Angel Bajana @angelbajana, owner and founder of Elev8tion Fitness @elev8tionfitness, currently with 5 locations and a mission statement of being “Results Driven. Passion Fueled.”

In this podcast episode, Angel and I relate our experiences as gym owners in Miami and the responsibilities that come with it. We also share the story behind how we developed our gym’s brand name and discuss the purpose and impact of our gym’s apparel. Additionally, we discuss the difference in work ethic between those in Miami and other parts of the country, revealing where we developed ours, as well as our position as leaders in developing, elevating, and building ourselves, our business, and our team- for the BETTER. 

Available tomorrow on all platforms. Link in bio.
